#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide.rst:144
#: c9c10d602c4c4142ab9c6237ae422767
msgid ""
"Do not panic. It may simply indicate that IOMMU-virtualization hasn’t "
"been activated in the BIOS or UEFI. Return to the `hardware requirements "
"<#hardware-requirements>`__ section to learn how to activate it. If the "
"setting is not configured correctly, it means that your hardware won’t be"
" able to leverage some Qubes security features, such as a strict "
"isolation of the networking and USB hardware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide.rst:146
#: f1e8d4e8970746ffbf9a56788a8d081c
msgid ""
"If the test passes, you will reach the installation summary screen. The "
"installer loads Xen right at the beginning. If you can see the "
"installer’s graphical screen, and you pass the compatibility check that "
"runs immediately afterward, Qubes OS is likely to work on your system!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/installation-guide.rst:148
#: 9f8aeb09698248dd9e05e124379f84a4
